\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Conditional probability distributions 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{P}\left(h\mid s\right)$
\end_inset

relating oil-field geophysical structure to drilling outcomes.
 (After 
