\begin_layout Standard
Given that Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Conditional BBAs"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 contains conditional bbas, we need additional information in order to obtain
 the marginals and the joint.
 The 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

prior
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 belief about the geological state 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{S}$
\end_inset

 is similarly given to us vacuously.
 This appears in Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Prior bbas on S"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
These values were originally provided by Strat 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Strat1994"
literal "false"

\end_inset

, who also gave us the Bayesian joint probability distributions 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{P}\left(h,s\right)$
\end_inset

 from Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Bayesian Oil-Field Struc"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 One surmises that Tables 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Conditional BBAs"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Prior bbas on S"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 were deliberately concocted to offer a ToE-equivalent to a set of Bayesian
 probabilities.
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Fuzzing
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 things up seems like a plausible proposition about the author's intent.
 That the values of the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

prior
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 bbas in Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Prior bbas on S"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 correspond to the marginal distributions in Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Bayesian Oil-Field Struc"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 probably was not coincidental.
\end_layout

